Subscribe to Australia’s daily coronavirus newsletter, and get the day’s must-reads and most important updates delivered straight to your inbox every weekday evening

Guardian Australia’s coronavirus newsletter is a daily wrap of all the news of the day, delivered after work each day to help keep you informed.

It gives you the top news headlines, most important developments of the day, latest health advice and information, as well as explainers and tips for helping you get through a global pandemic or self-isolation. It’s written each weekday by one of our staff and sent in the late afternoon to early evening, so you’ll get a the whole day’s developments wrapped up in one place.

Sign up now to get Australia’s day in coronavirus news explained straight to your inbox every weekday evening. See the latest Coronavirus: Australia at a glance here.

